.NOTES:
The following 3 commands set the document root
- docroot PATH
	- docroot: PATH
	- fileinfo: PATH + request.path
- alias PREFIX PATH
	- docroot = PATH
	- fileinfo = PATH + (request.path ~ s/PREFIX//)
- userdir
	- docroot = $HOME of user
	- fileinfo $HOME + s/request.path/^\/~.*?\//

